Recording Method:
"IRI (minted Nomen) with Nomen properties
- has nomen string https://www.rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/#P80068 
- assigned by agent http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/P80073  ($b and $2)
- date of usage http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/P80166 ($d)  
- has note on nomen (if $i) https://www.rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/#P80071
- has context of use http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/P80067 "Copyright or legal deposit number"
Justification for Mapping: Treat as identifier for manifestation in context of the copyright registration of a copy deposited with an agency.
Transformation Notes:
[Manifestation]-->rdamo:P30004-->[Nomen]-->rdand:P80068-->($a)
[Nomen]-->rdand P30004-->$b (string) 
if $2 containing "rocgpt:is present (only one valid code)
[Nomen}-->rdand P30004-->"R.O.C. Government Publications Catalogue (Taipei: Research, Development and Evaluation Commission, Executive Yuan)"
[Nomen]-->rdand P80166-->date in $d expressed as beginning of open timespan using whatever date structure is used for 008 or other date timespans. 
[Nomen]-->rdand:P80071-->($i)
[Nomen]-->rdand--> ""Copyright or legal deposit number"
